{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Restrict HGVs and agricultural vehicles on single carriageways to certain times",
        "additional_details": "This could:\r\n \r\n1) reduce the traffic congestion at key times during the day for other users of the roads (workers that have to commute by car/bus/van)\r\n2) reduce noise and tailpipe pollution\r\n3) increase the speed of traffic on these roads and improve people's time spent commuting to work\r\n",
        "background": "To improve the congestion on single carriageways in England, we think HGVs should be prohibited during the following hours:\r\n \r\nbetween 06:00 - 09:00hrs Mon - Sat\r\nbetween 18:00 - 21:00hrs Mon - Sat\r\nAll day Sunday - the only exception being if the cargo is perishable",
